%^BOLD%^-=%^RED%^Destruction Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

This domain allows the caster to create much destruction, just as the name implies.  The spells can affect both targets and their gear, depending on which spell is used.

The destruction domain contains the following spells:

True Strike, Rage, Disintegrate, Horrid Wilting, Greater Ruin

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Nilith, Khyron

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
